<h1>You Matter — A Gentle Check-In</h1>

<p class="lead">
This space is here to help you pause, breathe, and reflect.
If you are feeling overwhelmed, hopeless, or questioning your life’s value,
you are not alone — and these feelings can change.
</p>

<div class="notice">
<strong>Important:</strong>  
If you are in immediate danger or feel you might act on harmful thoughts,
please contact your local emergency number or a trusted person right now.
This tool is a supportive reflection — not a replacement for urgent help.
</div>

